{
  "stem": "4187.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was saying to my teacher that, if I'm not removed as captain and if I'm ever given another role as a Hungarian, the police will hear about it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, so, oh, of course, I was crying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I went home and told my mother that this dreadful thing has happened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, 'Please go straight in there and put this right.' And so my mother said, 'Well, sit down.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I've got something to tell you.'",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I went back-- I-- I stayed away from school for about three days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, when I went back, it was all changed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, I wasn't school captain anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- I had-- up till then, I had all, you know, top marks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had A's in everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And from then on, they always, on something, they gave me a-- a B, just so that it can't be said that I was a straight-A.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because straight A's were, you know, special.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, anyway, but then, this didn't last an awful long time, because the Germans came in within the year.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was then 12 when this happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And within a year, the Germans marched in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so [LAUGHS] the school days were over anyhow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I do remember that, from then on, after this happened, I had lost all confidence.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the-- the whole world had changed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, it's-- it-- it just-- it wasn't me anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and I really had to try and work out, well, exactly who am I?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Where do I belong?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It took a while to-- to-- to work that out, but I did.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
